Text: It prduces an ultrasound from your speakers, should work through headphones as well, but the sound will not be loud enough to have an effect. The whole point of it is to produce a sound at the frequency of the mosquito's wings' resonance. This makes it hard for the mosquitoes to fly. The performance of the utility also depends on the volume of the speakers. The louder the sound is the bigger the effect.
